ont-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Bear_and_the_Dragon" title="The Bear and the Dragon">The Bear and the Dragon</a></i> (2000)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Red_Rabbit" title="Red Rabbit">Red Rabbit</a></i> (2002)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Teeth_of_the_Tiger" title="The Teeth of the Tiger">The Teeth of the Tiger</a></i> (2003)</span></p>
